def test_200(self, client):
        """test that requests appear in the counter"""
        client.get("/200")
        metrics = client.get("/metrics").content.decode()
        assert (
            """starlette_requests_total{app_name=\"starlette\",method=\"GET\",path=\"/200\",status_code=\"200\"} 1.0"""
            in metrics
        )
